      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 56,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But turned back and acted treacherously like their fathers; They turned aside like a treacherous bow. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But turned back and acted treacherously like their fathers; They turned aside like a treacherous bow."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For they provoked Him with their high places And aroused His jealousy with their graven images. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For they provoked Him with their high places And aroused His jealousy with their graven images."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 59,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When God heard, He was filled with wrath And greatly abhorred Israel; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 59,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When God heard, He was filled with wrath And greatly abhorred Israel;"
